ch.nolix.core.container

Interface IContainer<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - The type of the elements of a IContainer.
    All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<E>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    List, Matrix, MatrixColumn, MatrixRow, ReadContainer, Stack, SubContainer

    public interface IContainer<E>
extends java.lang.Iterable<E>
    A IContainer can store several elements of a certain type. A IContainer is iterable. This interface provides no mutating methods.
    Author:
    Silvan Wyss
